{"tid":455301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(連登又炒車？)巴士先撞鐵欄 再將大陸女子撞跌","createTime":"2017-11-02T03:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T07:40:18.000Z","uid":45148,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8485e706a72a516ee8a3ec522cff8fa9b901d420","tid":455301,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"旺角彌敦道與亞皆老街交界交通黑點，下午發生恐怖車禍。來自廣東增城的姓黃少女(19歲)，持雙程證偕3名女友人來港，拖行李篋在旺角購物，下午4時許，一行在彌敦道與亞皆老街交界橫過彌敦道，步至北行線旺角滙豐大廈對開，因行人路太多人，僅能站於行人路邊等候前行。適時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一輛由紅磡往機場的A21號城巴由彌敦道左轉入亞皆老街，左車身突撞及路邊鐵欄，再將黃女撞跌</span></span>，車輪輾過其右小腿，腳掌位置登時皮開肉綻斷腳，她仍清醒，大叫「好痛」，其行李篋亦被撞爛，熱心途人紛紛上前安慰。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171101/mobile/bkn-20171101163500196-1101_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171101%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171101163500196-1101_00822_001.html&d=CknTApklNdW2AWKdhM4IHARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=08ce30c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171101/mobile/bkn-20171101163500196-1101_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n成班話司機無辜既 會唔會炒哂車<br />\n<br />\n講真果個位 長期人多<br />\n路人都迫到咁<br />\n架巴士轉得太入 就出事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：議事論事 非幫支那"},{"pid":"45cf9dfd9929948e39eda006006bab296122d803","tid":455301,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:14:49.000Z","msg":"支那人同廢老成日想快行到好出咪易俾人撞"},{"pid":"810815c413153a1224b94492c968014a03863455","tid":455301,"uid":26752,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"支那人沒有一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"c200962b4a24239e9fd8b28f33f698d3fa368b04","tid":455301,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"支那人沒有一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"ca85ae66504742200b3c9992d98957789af0e41f","tid":455301,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那人同廢老成日想快行到好出咪易俾人撞</blockquote><br />\n唔排除支那人企到好出<br />\n但巴士都係撞左鐵欄先喎<br />\n<br />\n只係講可能兩面都有錯"},{"pid":"1d20e6eb5c97693fc059969213f30d035f6c139f","tid":455301,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"明明新聞尋日都講先撞欄喎，點解會炒車<br />\n冇睇內文？"},{"pid":"4544ae575a8b8c52e4d26089ded382bb0546b209","tid":455301,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"我反而想知狗巴要賠幾多？幾百粒實走唔甩"},{"pid":"192082dc9cf7d2b4a52ce23f0bb4ab6c1928ff51","tid":455301,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而想知狗巴要賠幾多？幾百粒實走唔甩</blockquote><br />\n起碼果班怕支那婦走醫院數既人可以放心<br />\n巴士公司一定要埋單"},{"pid":"6cc33ee135265a6e398d393c8595fc21cad8926b","tid":455301,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明新聞尋日都講先撞欄喎，點解會炒車<br />\n冇睇內文？</blockquote><br />\n我有睇內文<br />\n你無追尋日d post <br />\n話咩 害死司機<br />\n司機無辜"},{"pid":"05df80390010ab7fee295eb62f5149c4bcfa12c2","tid":455301,"uid":4493,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而想知狗巴要賠幾多？幾百粒實走唔甩</blockquote><br />\n$0<br />\n<br />\n因為係城巴"},{"pid":"b7b1c119712407abf8667a01c71c912f667c5dd2","tid":455301,"uid":152934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"炒咩車 細細個老豆老母就教等過馬路唔好企咁出 <br />\n難道各位連登仔係執返黎 冇老豆老母教?"},{"pid":"d135ada4226bbec5a296b6abf5d66c653c3907a6","tid":455301,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"又係城巴.."},{"pid":"b12eba617d2669db37120077ca494b8e31e33129","tid":455301,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢有無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}